      # Commands

      ## relay.turnOn()

      Turns on the voltage controlled by the relay.

      ## relay.turnOff()

      Turns off the voltage controlled by the relay.

      ## relay.isOn()

      Returns the state of the relay, if it is currently on.

      ## relay.turnOff()

      Returns the state of the relay, if it is currently off.

